These are Puzzles for 3x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: singing, puzzles, camping, photography, chess
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: disaster, western, sports, musical, romance
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: parkour, climbing, badminton, snowboarding, sailing
 1. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 2. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who's hobby is chess##2
 5. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 6. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 7. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
 9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the person watching romance movies is the person who's sport is sailing##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
12. the person who's sport is badminton is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |      5      |
| Hobby         | puzzles    | camping  | chess | singing    | photography |
| Movie-Genre   | western     | sports   | musical | romance | disaster   |
| Sport         | parkour | climbing | snowboarding  | sailing | badminton        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: chess, reading, gardening, fishing, skydiving
The people have 5 different jobs:  manager, social-worker, fisherman, writer, bartender
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cricket, weightlifting, rowing, skiing, biathlon
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is in an odd position##4
 2. the bartender is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's sport is skiing##2
 3. the bartender is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the social-worker##1
 6. the person who's hobby is chess is in the middle##1
 7. the manager is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 8. the social-worker is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
10. the bartender is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
11. the writer is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
12. the person who's sport is skiing is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1        |        2        |     3      |         4          |     5     |
| Hobby   | fishing    | reading         | chess | skydiving        | gardening   |
| Job     | social-worker | fisherman | writer  | bartender | manager |
| Sport   | rowing       | biathlon      | skiing   | weightlifting           | cricket      |

