.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk, sprite, juice, almond-milk
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: tennis, volleyball, cricket, water-polo, surfing
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, train, motorbike, bus, skateboard
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the person driving the train is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 3. the person drinking juice is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 5. the person drinking milk is between the person driving the train and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 6. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 8. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an even position##4
10. the person drinking sprite is the person driving the skateboard##1
11. the person who's sport is tennis is the person driving the motorbike##1
12. the person driving the bus is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person driving the skateboard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2     |     3      |       4       |     5      |
| Beverage    | sprite | soy-milk    | juice   | milk          | almond-milk      |
| Sport       | cricket    | surfing | volleyball       | water-polo | tennis |
| Transport   | skateboard     | bus     | train | car          | motorbike     |

