.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: romance, western, scientific, documentary, crime
5 different pets are kept: ferret, horse, fish, goldfish, snake
The people use 5 different means of transport: tram, snowmobile, airplane, bus, jet-ski
 1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
 2. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
 4. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 5. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
 7. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 9. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4
10. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
11. the person watching romance movies is on the far left or far right##3
12. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | crime    | scientific  | documentary | western |
| Pet           | goldfish | horse    | fish | snake  | ferret    |
| Transport     | jet-ski      | airplane | bus    | snowmobile    | tram    |

