.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: hip-hop, electronic, house, reggae, gospel
There are 5 different nationalities: mexican, nigerian, australian, polish, argentine
The people use 5 different means of transport: roller, trike, boat, quad-bike, bus
 1. the person driving the trike is the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 3. the person driving the boat is in an even position##4
 4. the fan of gospel is the polish##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the roller and the fan of gospel##2
 6. the fan of electronic is in the middle##1
 7. the mexican is on the left of the nigerian##1
 8. the person driving the roller is on the right of the australian##1
 9. the argentine is on the far right##1
10. the australian is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
11. the fan of reggae is the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |    5    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | hip-hop        | electronic    | house      | reggae  |
| Nationality   | polish | australian    | mexican | nigerian | argentine |
| Transport     | trike   | quad-bike | roller | boat      | bus   |

