 9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
11. the fan of r&b is the person driving the quad-bike##1
12. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3

