 3. the person eating cabbage is on the far right##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 5. the fan of salsa is in an even position##4
 6. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
 7. the fan of reggae is the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking 7up and the fan of classical##2
 9. the person eating potato is in an odd position##4
10. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |
| Beverage      | tea    | almond-milk | coffee   | mirinda  | 7up |
| Food          | potato    | artichoke  | cauliflower | grapes | cabbage  |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | salsa    | classical      | r&b   | disco |

